BT /F2 9.50 Tf 0.040 0.340 0.780 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 620.50 Tm (SAY \(read this aloud\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 604.50 Tm (To really appreciate Spring Boot, you have to feel the pain it removed. So let me take you back in) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 589.30 Tm (time. The Spring framework came out in 2003, and it was genuinely brilliant - it gave us clean,) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 574.10 Tm (well-organised code. But there was a catch: just getting a project to start was slow and frustrating.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 553.90 Tm (Picture this. Before you could write a single line of useful code, you had to do all of this by hand.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 538.70 Tm (You wrote pages and pages of XML configuration. You manually connected every object to every) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 523.50 Tm (other object. You separately downloaded and installed a web server called Tomcat, configured it,) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 508.30 Tm (and deployed your app into it. And you hand-picked the version of every library and prayed they all) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 493.10 Tm (worked together.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 472.90 Tm (Honestly, teams would spend an entire day just to get an empty project running. A whole day,) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 457.70 Tm (before any real work. That is the frustration Spring Boot was built, in 2014, to wipe away. So as we) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 442.50 Tm (go through today, every feature of Boot is really an answer to one of these old pains. Keep that in) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 427.30 Tm (mind.) Tj ET
0.040 0.520 1.000 rg 58.00 412.10 3.00 214.40 re f
