BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 621.10 Tm (Manual wiring - you connected every dependency yourself, and if you forgot one, the app crashed) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 605.90 Tm (at runtime, not before. No built-in server - you had to build a special file, install Tomcat, configure) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 590.70 Tm (it, and deploy into it; four slow manual steps. Version conflicts - you matched the versions of) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 575.50 Tm (Spring, the JSON library, the logging library, all by hand, and one wrong combination caused the) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 560.30 Tm (famous 'dependency hell'. And repeated boilerplate - the same setup code copied into every new) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 545.10 Tm (project before you could even begin.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 524.90 Tm (Now, here is what I want you to notice about all four. Every single one is the same kind of work for) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 509.70 Tm (almost every project. It is boring, repetitive setup that does not change much from app to app.) Tj ET
0.040 0.520 1.000 rg 58.00 494.50 3.00 184.00 re f
