BT /F1 10.50 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 453.10 Tm (should every developer do it by hand? The framework should just do it by default, and let you change) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 438.70 Tm (only the rare bits that differ. That idea is called 'convention over configuration', and it is the soul of) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 424.30 Tm (Spring Boot. Say it clearly - it ties the whole session together.) Tj ET
