BT /F1 10.50 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 723.60 Tm (is the self-starting ignition and the auto-tuning. The engine was always powerful, but now it starts) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 709.20 Tm (instantly and tunes itself. So everything they learn about core Spring still applies - Boot just means less) Tj ET
