BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 290.60 Tm (service to do the actual thinking - the business logic. The service asks a repository to fetch or save) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 275.40 Tm (data. And the repository talks to the database. Then the answer travels all the way back along the) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 260.20 Tm (same path to the browser.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 240.00 Tm (So the chain is: browser, front desk, controller, service, repository, database - and back. Notice) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 224.80 Tm (each box has exactly one clear job.) Tj ET
